{"id": "1349652563418415104", "channel_id": "1349652563418415104", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感謝各位守密人的支持！\n《忘卻前夜》OST：阿格里帕EP·坎布里安的晨曦，今日發佈～歡迎大家收聽、下載及分享～如果有基於OST的二次創作，也歡迎分享給我們！ （二創請遵照同人規則，OST內容請勿商用）\n\n《忘卻前夜》OST：阿格里帕EP·坎布里安的晨曦\n當河谷的第一道晨光照入迷宮之時，千足千子沉睡千年的公主，迎來了她最後一位信徒。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n規劃：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Agrippa EP·Cambrian Dawn》 was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n《Morimens》OST：《Agrippa EP·Cambrian Dawn》 \nAs the first light of dawn touched the valley maze, the millennia-sleeping Princess Qianzuqianzi welcomed her final follower.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-03-13T07:57:26.451000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "wish", "emoji_id": "1236951537788649492", "count": 9}], "attachments": [{"id": "1349652563754225735", "filename": "EP__.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 345050, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349652563418415104/1349652563754225735/EP__.jpg?ex=69cccfe6&is=69cb7e66&hm=2687ea83f65238235032d68f749fd275ec01491697b3b158ff688541adc8f542&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349652563418415104", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：阿格里帕EP·坎布里安的晨曦", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349652742112809004", "channel_id": "1349652563418415104", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "1.迷宮逃亡-labyrinth escape-\n戰略性撤退雖可恥，但有用。\nStrategic retreat is shameful, but useful.", "timestamp": "2025-03-13T07:58:09.055000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349652741705695232", "filename": "1.-labyrinth_escape-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 29801972, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349652563418415104/1349652741705695232/1.-labyrinth_escape-.wav?ex=69ccd010&is=69cb7e90&hm=3afd285f2b7a7f7446fa662b6a5236bc15465821c376377a8e45ab0c6f4bc8c0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349652563418415104", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：阿格里帕EP·坎布里安的晨曦", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349652841341390899", "channel_id": "1349652563418415104", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "2.猜謎遊戲-boring game-\n來陪我玩個遊戲吧，放心，沒那麼危險，只是為了打發這無聊的時間。\nCome play a game with me, don't worry, it's not that dangerous, just to kill time.", "timestamp": "2025-03-13T07:58:32.713000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349652840863367221", "filename": "2.-boring_game-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 20860946, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349652563418415104/1349652840863367221/2.-boring_game-.wav?ex=69ccd028&is=69cb7ea8&hm=cd799edca1fbc789c79b93ac2bff6e2eb5ff8f8af68510a9225031d2d0daf9b6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349652563418415104", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：阿格里帕EP·坎布里安的晨曦", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349652976112762923", "channel_id": "1349652563418415104", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "3.過往餘輝-past glow-\n曾經的輝煌已經過去，只剩下記憶中的斷壁殘垣。\nThe past glory is gone, only the broken walls and ruins in memory remain.", "timestamp": "2025-03-13T07:59:04.845000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349652975576154163", "filename": "3.-past_glow-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 39916508, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349652563418415104/1349652975576154163/3.-past_glow-.wav?ex=69ccd048&is=69cb7ec8&hm=b25489779940df739138d24eb249f6cd3f1883533a19443ce234ecf90a1d475d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349652563418415104", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：阿格里帕EP·坎布里安的晨曦", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349653364270698537", "channel_id": "1349652563418415104", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "4.黃沙之下-under the sand-\n鮮血，殺戮，改變……埋藏在無盡黃沙下的，是時間長河中殘酷而常見的歷史。\nBlood, killing, change... buried under the endless yellow sand is the cruel and common history in the long river of time.", "timestamp": "2025-03-13T08:00:37.389000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349653363708526633", "filename": "4.-under_the_sand-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 49429530, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349652563418415104/1349653363708526633/4.-under_the_sand-.wav?ex=69ccd0a5&is=69cb7f25&hm=fd4daac61f8de387322a7a4450767be90e9e2e8ad7b08ce5b815f426bc580178&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349652563418415104", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：阿格里帕EP·坎布里安的晨曦", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1349653395073667145", "channel_id": "1349652563418415104", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "5.二人的流星-meteor of our-\n英雄和公主奔跑在夜幕下，腳下的砂礫訴說著生的喜悅。那顆封閉千年的心，也隨著流星的劃過，緩緩地開始跳動。\nThe hero and the princess ran under the night, and the gravel under their feet told the joy of life. The heart that had been closed for a thousand years also slowly began to beat as the meteor passed by.", "timestamp": "2025-03-13T08:00:44.733000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1349653394993844246", "filename": "5.-meteor_of_our-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 37231322, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1349652563418415104/1349653394993844246/5.-meteor_of_our-.wav?ex=69ccd0ac&is=69cb7f2c&hm=80a338f30be3ace2d7467d3316c80c056f85de48f15b9491f6be76dcbfc8d92f&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1349652563418415104", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "《忘卻前夜》OST：阿格里帕EP·坎布里安的晨曦", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
